query_gender
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_gender

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_gender -  This method returns the gender of the deity.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_gender(string deity)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^deity%^RESET%^ - the deity name
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the gender of the deity

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/deity_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the gender of the deity.  The gender is the same
as used elsehwere in the game.  0 for neuter, 1 for male and 2 for female.
.EP

